Telkom has unveiled its Big Deal for September 2018, which includes mobile data and a MiFi router. The SmartInternet package features the following: The Huawei MiFi router features a 1,500mAh battery and can achieve download speeds of up to 150Mbps. It also supports up to 10 device connections. The inclusive data bundle on SmartInternet plans will not carry over to the following month, and will expire at the end of each month, stated Telkom in its terms and conditions. An out-of-bundle rate of R0.30 per MB shall apply on SmartInternet offers, it added. The deal is valid until 30 September 2018, or while stocks last. <span data-mce-type="bookmark" style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;" class="mce_SELRES_start">ï»¿</span>